{"id":139204,"type":6,"name":"オンナミチ","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/0d/e7/139204_ssPHH.jpg","summary":"　　元カレからお金をダマし取られるという、人生最悪の誕生日を迎えたレコード会社勤務･山口梨花。そんな彼女の前に、ヒョウ柄のワンピースを着たオバちゃんが突然、白煙とともに現れる。20年後の山口梨花と名乗るオバちゃんは、飲み屋でビール瓶に足を滑らせ、無念の死を遂げてしまったことを悔んで、人生をやり直すために未来から現れたという。今の自分とはスタイルも身なりも絶望的に違う、未来の自分と一緒に、恋に仕事に、アラサー女子の人生やり直し大作戦が始まった。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>女人之路</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期二</li><li><span>集数: </span>8</li><li><span>开始: </span>2015年8月4日</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>语言: </span>日语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>29分钟</li><li><span>电视台: </span>NHK</li><li><span>首播地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>www.nhk.or.jp/pyd/onnamichi/</li><li><span>导演: </span>村松弘之</li><li><span>编剧: </span>田中ひろみ / 坪田文</li><li><span>主演: </span>片瀬那奈 / 渡辺えり / 徳重聡 / 市川由衣 / 小野ゆり子 / 渡部豪太 / MEGUMI / 浅見れいな / 合田雅吏 / 羽場裕一 / 金田明夫</li>","collection":{"on_hold":2},"eps":[{"id":545599,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545599","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":545600,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545600","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":545601,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545601","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":545602,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545602","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":545603,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545603","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":545604,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545604","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":545605,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545605","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":545606,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/545606","type":0,"sort":8,"nam